      "review_summary": "This PR changes builtin memory status to infer vector-store readiness from persisted `vectorDims` metadata and adds a seeded status-only manager regression test.\n\nPR surface: Source +1, Tests +124. Total +125 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. by source inspection: plain `memory status` uses a status-purpose manager, skips vector probing unless deep/index is requested, and current main renders undefined `storeAvailable` as `Vector store: unknown`. I did not run a real indexed CLI repro because this review is read-only.",
